6968:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
6969:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h5xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be enabled with conversion on going on group regular,
